LeConte, by Chaudoir (1868b: 296), confirmed by Erwin (1970a: 144).
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="477" pageNumber="478">
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Brachynus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="477" pageNumber="478" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gracilis">
